      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Using personal data in your business or other organisation after the transition period
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What action you need to take regarding data protection and data flows with the EU/EEA after the end of the transition period.
</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
